title: Jasmine Tookes and Stella Maxwell support fellow Victoria's Secret Angel Taylor Hill
text:
Once a Victoria's Secret Angel, always a Victoria's Secret Angel.

Jasmine Tookes and Stella Maxwell came out to support their fellow Angel, Taylor Hill, at her Boohoo Tea Party in Los Angeles.

The models turned out Sunday in chic outfits from Taylor's collection with the fashion company.

Angels for life: Jasmine Tookes (left) and Stella Maxwell (right) came out to support Taylor Hill (center) at the release of her Boohoo collection, Sunday in Los Angeles

Jasmine, 28, flashed just a bit of her toned stomach, in a matching beige co-ord set.

The fuzzy trousers were paired with a cropped, high-neck top and black pointed toe stilettos. The set retails for $20 on the shop's website.

She looked head to toe chic with a sleek hairdo styled down and a perfect face of makeup.

Co-ord: Jasmine paired fuzzy trousers with a cropped, high-neck top and black pointed toe stilettos. The set retails for $20 on the shop's website

Chic: She looked head to toe chic with a sleek hairdo styled down and a perfect face of makeup

While Stella opted for a dress from the collection that also is on sale for $20.

Her emerald green dress featured a plunging v-neckline and ruffled, off the shoulder straps.

For accessories she opted just for gold strappy stilettos.

The 29-year-old Belgian born model, cut an old-Hollywood glamorous display with her blonde locks styled to her left side in very loose curls.

Old Hollywood: Her emerald green dress featured a plunging v-neckline and ruffled, off the shoulder straps

Glamorous: The 29-year-old Belgian born model, cut an old-Hollywood glamorous display with her blonde locks styled to her left side in very loose curls

They posed with the collection creator at the event, who also wore pieces from her line.

Taylor was in head to toe pink, in a wide leg trouser and matching oversized blazer. The pants retail for $20.

Underneath was her fluffy white crop top, with rhinestone covered straps, is part of a midi skirt set, that retails for $28.

The 23-year-old teamed the look with blush pink stilettos and a long loose wave hairdo.
